Package: pmxcopula
Type: Package
Title: Copula Evaluation in Pharmacometric Anaylsis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Laura B. Zwep, Yuchen Guo
Maintainer: Yuchen Guo <iguoyuchen@outlook.com>
Description: Facilitate the evaluation of copula model for virtual population generation in pharmacometric analysis.
    Calculate the overlap metric based on the 2-dimensional densities of the observed and simulated populations.
    Conduct the donut VPC check of the copula model.
